âœ… Kerberos Logon Events to Look For:
Event ID	Description
4624	Successful logon (Kerberos or NTLM)
4768	A Kerberos authentication ticket (TGT) was requested
4769	A Kerberos service ticket was requested
4770	A Kerberos TGT was renewed
4771	Kerberos pre-authentication failed
4776	NTLM authentication request


Rum CMD as administrator

# Get recent Kerberos-related logon events
Get-WinEvent -FilterHashtable @{
    LogName = 'Security';
    ID = 4768, 4769, 4770, 4771
} | Select-Object TimeCreated, Id, Message | Format-List

Optional: filter for a specific user:

Get-WinEvent -FilterHashtable @{
    LogName = 'Security';
    ID = 4768, 4769, 4770, 4771
} | Where-Object { $_.Message -like '*galeano*' } | Select TimeCreated, Id, Message


